#: ../files.rst:122
msgid "If you want your split file segments available outside of your OpenShot project, or want to copy all your video assets to one place, you can do this with the **Export Files** dialog. Simply :kbd:`Ctrl+Click` to select all the files you like, then :kbd:`Right Click` and choose :guilabel:`Export Files`. In the dialog that appears, choose a destination folder, and click :guilabel:`Export`."
