#: ../files.rst:127
msgid "NOTE: This will export each file or file segment using its **original video profile** (width, height, framerate, aspect ratio, etc...). It also supports any :ref:`split_clip_ref` (described above). For example, if you have split a long video file into many different segments (and named them), you can now export all the segments as separate video files (using the original file's video profile)."
msgstr ""

